{"tid":1589412,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(軸心內政) 外交部：阿富汗塔利班代表近日到中国溝通","createTime":"2019-09-23T09:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T03:01:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"71a82b0548fefaa024bdf78b95ef18a2ee471cbf","tid":1589412,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:31:05.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部證實阿富汗塔利班的代表團，近日到中國溝通。外交部發言人耿爽說，阿富汗塔利班駐多哈政治辦事處主任巴拉達爾，以及多名助手，近日來華溝通，中國外交部的主管官員同巴拉達爾，就阿富汗的形勢以及推進阿富汗和平問題進程交換意見。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽說，中方始終高度關注阿富汗的局勢，始終致力推動阿富汗的和平和解進程，一直同涉及阿富汗的有關各方，保持接觸和溝通。他又說，中方一貫堅定支持「阿人主導、阿人所有」的廣泛包容性的和平和解進程，希望美國和阿富汗塔利班保持談判勢頭，支持對話談判，早日實現民族和解與和平穩定，中方也將繼續發揮建設性作用。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482104-20190923.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482104-20190923.htm&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK6wpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=2d638bfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482104-20190923.htm&h=3c3c48ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482104-20190923.htm</a>"},{"pid":"193faf0bf1706a543023c619be49259c13450bad","tid":1589412,"uid":105578,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:32:16.000Z","msg":"真係cls到唔知講咩好"},{"pid":"180a226580b00f8022f4a3600b4bcc0818dcfa9f","tid":1589412,"uid":321837,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:34:31.000Z","msg":"接受新一輪嘅恐襲行動指示."},{"pid":"1dd46793b9328f7ab314afa3433f61495d1c1f63","tid":1589412,"uid":36134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:36:29.000Z","msg":"越黎越猖狂"},{"pid":"557810f1f0f4235aff988ce97c49cd9e437d4d81","tid":1589412,"uid":290429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:54:23.000Z","msg":"CLS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078d338ad8b925cc5f2d0d549ab67c68f2ace385",